
  ------------  The Moons over Darkwind ------------------

  	MAGENTA: The wisdom moon.
		 Powers include identification and surreal
		 transendental effects.  This would include
		 travel, item lore, clairvoyance.

	RED    : The blood moon.
		 Powers include harm, death, destruction.
		 This would include all attack spells.

	GREEN  : The natural moon.
		 Powers include natural force manipulation.
		 This would include healing in any way.


  ----------------------------------------------------------
